data.description: Take a look at this adorable 4-bed, 2-bath gem in highly desired Ocean Springs! Loads of natural sunlight flood this spacious yet cozy home. Tucked away on a mostly wooded street, it comes complete with a charming fireplace, tray ceilings, , roomy bedrooms with lush new carpets, , and a  2-car garage. Take your pick between a private well or hook up to community water—it's your call! The fully fenced in backyard is perfect for families, pet lovers, gardeners and entertaining. With multiple public boat launches around, and the Lake Mars pier, you can fish or just relax and soak in those jaw-dropping Gulf of Mexico sunsets. Convenient to everything including Downtown Ocean Springs, shops, restaurants, hospitals, award winning schools, and easy commutes down Hwy 90 and I-10 to local military bases and major industry employers! Your coastal haven awaits!
